title: ADVENTURE TIME 021 (2013) (4 covers) (digital) (Minutemen-InnerD
description: It's another crazy adventure with our favorite heroes of Ooo. Join Finn and Jake as they protect their friends from the Ice King... who isn't really a bad guy... he's just kind of sad sometimes. But that's okay because Finn and Jake aren't sad, and that's what makes them our heroes! Jump into a fantastical world, with adventures, lessons, and sometimes princess farts.
